{"tid":1577542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想做魔法師既朋友，唔該練下lv先好開技","createTime":"2019-09-17T18:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T13:01:15.000Z","uid":222524,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c894a2cfb267bb13786c384d515cf8a6318fa95","tid":1577542,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:08:21.000Z","msg":"冇錯，魔法師係好勁既職業<br />\n但都係好高技術既職業<br />\n見到有人吹風想提升魔法師人數<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力，我唔會阻你<br />\n但希望想轉職做魔法師既手足，趁呢半個月，練下lv，練下準繩度，先打10.1活動副本<br />\n識有人對上個次被自己友tk咗<br />\n雖然除非唔到係咪鬼做<br />\n但要知道我地自己友冇厚甲，中咗好傷架<br />\n盡量對準少少，有把握先扔，好唔好"},{"pid":"4e3c590835527828d0f391dfb83ee7256413cbad","tid":1577542,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:47:19.000Z","msg":"練習臂力 掉網球 掉棒球<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b118e109067d3da0840060b70f5151698862eb0","tid":1577542,"uid":291321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:59:24.000Z","msg":"好多初級魔法師力都唔夠， 唔該交畀大力魔法師做， 唔使嘥曬啲嘢"},{"pid":"7428f18b116f433714c947e26366fd15ee6e530a","tid":1577542,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:00:44.000Z","msg":"根本好多人手腦協調能力不足， 點樣練習都冇用"},{"pid":"f743456ae1323161e29b3be240f4f6f7dce486bc","tid":1577542,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e3c590835527828d0f391dfb83ee7256413cbad","tid":1577542,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:47:19.000Z","msg":"練習臂力 掉網球 掉棒球<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:21:21.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"dd1688d9377958f1e7c4ece39d6186ad89de5740","tid":1577542,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b118e109067d3da0840060b70f5151698862eb0","tid":1577542,"uid":291321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:59:24.000Z","msg":"好多初級魔法師力都唔夠， 唔該交畀大力魔法師做， 唔使嘥曬啲嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:21:52.